descriptionHtml: Clever Share is a Sharing Application.
descriptionShort: Clever Share - Sharing was never this much easy
title: Clever Share

creator: Tarpara Technologies
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the sharing world!!!

We have developed Clever Share to make your sharing experience very smooth. Now you don't need data cable to access your data across multiple devices.

We are providing below services using in Clever Share application.

• Download in mobile: Go to My Documents screen from sidebar, you will be able to see the list of documents upload by you on server. Select one or more documents which you want to download in your mobile and click on download button showing at bottom left side. You will be able to download maximum 10 files at a time.

• Download in computer: Go to My Documents screen from sidebar, you will be able to see the list of documents upload by you on server. Select one or more documents which you want to download in computer and then click on floating button showing at bottom right and select the option Download in computer. You will be redirected to a QR code scanner screen, now open https://web.clevershare.in/ on computer where you want to download and select Download option from top and scan the QR code, your download will be started soon in the computer.

• Upload from mobile: Go to My Documents screen from sidebar, you will be able to see floating button at bottom right, click on it and select the option Upload from mobile. You will be redirected to a Upload Screen, now open select one or more files you want to upload and click on Upload Files button. You will be able to upload maximum 10.00 MB of files on server at a time.

• Upload from computer: Select one or more files from computer which you want to upload from your computer. Go to My Documents screen from sidebar, you will be able to see floating button at bottom right, click on it and select the option Upload from computer. You will be redirected to a QR code scanner screen, now open https://web.clevershare.in/ on computer and select Upload option from top and scan the QR code, your upload will be started soon in the computer.

Happy Sharing...
